: Kdr high-threshold, non-inactivating K current

NEURON {
     SUFFIX kdr
     USEION k READ ek WRITE ik
     RANGE gk, ik
}

UNITS {
     (S)  = (siemens)
     (mV) = (millivolt)
     (mA) = (milliamp)
}

PARAMETER { gk = 42e-4 (S/cm2) }

